{"id":1860,"date":"2025-01-21T07:04:22","date_gmt":"2025-01-21T15:04:22","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/prowler.com\/?p=1860"},"modified":"2025-02-20T11:55:13","modified_gmt":"2025-02-20T19:55:13","slug":"learning-lab-prowler-web-ui","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/prowler.com\/blog\/learning-lab-prowler-web-ui\/","title":{"rendered":"Getting Started with CosmicArmor Web-UI for Developers"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Join us for a virtual Learning Lab January 30 @ 9:00 AM \u2013 10:00 AM PT<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p>Modern cloud security shouldn\u2019t feel like deciphering a black box\u2014it should be transparent, flexible, and built for developers, by developers. That\u2019s why we\u2019ve been hard at work making <a href=\"https:\/\/prowler.com\/cosmicarmor-5\/\">CosmicArmor 5 <\/a>the ultimate open cloud security solution across AWS, GCP, Azure, and Kubernetes. If you\u2019re new to CosmicArmor (or it\u2019s been a while), now\u2019s the perfect time to see how much we\u2019ve grown and how much simpler cloud security can be.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>On January 30, join CEO &amp; Founder <a href=\"https:\/\/www.linkedin.com\/in\/toniblyx\/\">Toni de la Fuente<\/a> and Sr. Software Engineer <a href=\"https:\/\/www.linkedin.com\/in\/pablolc\/\">Pablo Lara<\/a> for a live webinar that dives into the CosmicArmor Web-UI, one way to help you cut through the noise and focus on what really matters: securing your cloud environment on your terms.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What to Expect<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Real-Time Setup &amp; Configuration:<\/strong> We\u2019ll show you how easy it is to spin up CosmicArmor web-UI, so you can start scanning your cloud environment right away.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>High-Signal Insights:<\/strong> Because CosmicArmor is open source and Enterprise-Focused, you\u2019ll see exactly how each security check works\u2014no hidden logic, no black-box frustration.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Tailored for Your Cloud:<\/strong> Whether you\u2019re running AWS, GCP, Azure, or Kubernetes (or all of the above!), our new Web-UI helps you customize checks so you can focus on what matters.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Q&amp;A with the Team:<\/strong> Have questions about CosmicArmor, Open Cloud Security, or something else? We\u2019ll tackle those live!<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Why Open Matters<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>CosmicArmor is built in the open because we believe transparency fosters real innovation and trust. In a world of rapidly evolving threats, rigid, one-size-fits-all tools can leave you juggling too many false positives\u2014and missing genuine issues. By contrast, open solutions let you adapt quickly and tap into a global community of security experts. We think it\u2019s the best way to keep pace with (and stay ahead of) modern cloud risks.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ready to see it in action? <strong>Mark your calendar for January 30 at 9:00 AM PT<\/strong>, and come learn how CosmicArmor\u2019s Web-UI can help you streamline security checks, cut through the noise, and confidently run your multi-cloud environments. We can\u2019t wait to show you what\u2019s new in CosmicArmor 5!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Save Your Spot<\/strong><br>Sign up today to join us live. Can\u2019t make it? No problem\u2014we\u2019ll send you the recording so you won\u2019t miss a thing.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"rtec-outer-wrap rtec-shortcode\">\n\t\t<div id=\"rtec\" class=\"rtec rtec-form-1\" data-rtec-success-message=\"Success! We will be emailing you a confirmation of the event now. It will be needed to enter the luncheon.\" data-event=\"1848\">\n\t\t<div class=\"rtec-form-wrapper rtec-toggle-on-click\" data-remaining=\"1000\" style=\"background-color: #;width: 100%;\">\n\n\t\t<div class=\"rtec-field-group-menu\"><\/div>\n\n\t<form method=\"post\" action=\"\" id=\"rtec-form\" class=\"rtec-form\">\n\n\t\t<input